{"tid":2000063,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"冷凍LAN線分享","createTime":"2020-05-03T15:00:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-12T05:52:29.000Z","uid":4672,"like":4,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"4abab95853080bc549e4b6229ac446580dfdba54","tid":2000063,"uid":4672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T15:00:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/AmbagoAudio/posts/2015038021965058\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FAmbagoAudio%2Fposts%2F2015038021965058&d=LQBsT8b49a%2FdXTDbQfnWX8orGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=33d4a0b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/AmbagoAudio/posts/2015038021965058</a><br />\n多謝各位師兄的支持, 小店facebook專頁快到2000 Like , 為答謝師兄們一直的支持, 小店推出冷凍 Cat 8 Lan線優惠。<br />\n冷凍Cat 8 Lan 線採用經冷凍內地企業級頭:$360 (1.5M) 限量20條<br />\n冷凍Cat 8 Lan 線採用Telegartner Cat 6A頭:$480 (1.5M) 限量15條<br />\n冷凍Cat 8 Lan 線採用Telegartner Cat 8頭:$580 (1.5M) 限量15條<br />\n<br />\n+$30 順丰郵寄<br />\n如要訂制長度, 交付時間將額外需要3天, 每0.5M +$70, 2M起做。<br />\n<br />\n內地Cat 8 Lan 線相信有唔少師兄都試過, 聲音比一般Lan 線是較好的。小店抱住發燒的精神, 特意把這線作冷凍, 發現質素大大提昇, 於是再嘗試採用德國Telegartner 的Lan 頭試試, 結果係點?<br />\n<br />\n就係成為小店誠意推薦的高質入門Lan線, 於小店試音室作為Apodidae Switch 與 dCS Network Bridge 之間的Lan 線, 聲音爽快, 動態、静度及延伸都不俗, 而且有點肉地。<br />\n<br />\n可能有師兄會覺得鼓油貴話雞, 但以成品線的總定價來說, 應該還是不二之選。小店正煩惱如何定價, 因Telegartner頭一對$250﹐加上冷凍的成本比線本身高於數倍。<br />\n<br />\n近排小店的某個帖非常火熱, 如未能接受冷凍的燒友或非發燒友, 請高抬貴手。小店認為非善意或沒意義的回覆, 恕删, 謝謝。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sMYwO2Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsMYwO2Z.jpg&h=e44aaf09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b5dT2n0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb5dT2n0.jpg&h=bc0203ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e4CNnn0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe4CNnn0.jpg&h=8781b844&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">我屌</span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"603bf01c813dba844f1ede899a88a36779573397","tid":2000063,"uid":135475,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T15:02:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">內地</span>企業級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15f1749089539272d1bcb7560faa93cd562a3660","tid":2000063,"uid":190264,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T15:04:49.000Z","msg":"d音響撚 玩既唔係音質<br />\n玩既係同d同圈人吹水扮鳩哂金耳仔既成就感"},{"pid":"c6b6e9787205d7a627f1b855850119c1e53a7943","tid":2000063,"uid":229100,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"15f1749089539272d1bcb7560faa93cd562a3660","tid":2000063,"uid":190264,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T15:04:49.000Z","msg":"d音響撚 玩既唔係音質<br />\n玩既係同d同圈人吹水扮鳩哂金耳仔既成就感"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T15:07:00.000Z","msg":"你錯晒<br />\n係玄學<br />\n我比條外皮好撚粗既線佢同佢講係德國頂級音響CAT6線<br />\n佢用完都會話好好聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edc642baac5a4bd7b525934e8a43f80815fa1396","tid":2000063,"uid":4672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"15f1749089539272d1bcb7560faa93cd562a3660","tid":2000063,"uid":190264,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T15:04:49.000Z","msg":"d音響撚 玩既唔係音質<br />\n玩既係同d同圈人吹水扮鳩哂金耳仔既成就感"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T15:07:29.000Z","msg":"唔買冷凍LAN線，音響級SSD的話<br />\n哪有談資同其他燒友吹水 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a3b0e40afb0768534d1da8c2a6b9ea9ff4c9c14","tid":2000063,"uid":4672,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"603bf01c813dba844f1ede899a88a36779573397","tid":2000063,"uid":135475,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T15:02:19.000Z","msg":"<span style